Perfect! EAS has successfully configured your project and generated a valid `projectId`. 

**Select "All"** to configure both iOS and Android platforms at once. This will set up everything you need for building both platforms.

Use the arrow keys to select **"All"** and press Enter.

After this completes, you'll be ready to build:

**For testing (APK):**
```bash
eas build --platform android --profile preview
```

**For production (AAB + IPA):**
```bash
eas build --platform all --profile production
```

The configuration will set up the necessary credentials and build profiles for both platforms.